CCCCC                   OCTOBER 2002.  ADD ICAPSW, ICAPTY TO CALL LIST
     1                  ICAPSW,ICAPTY,IFORSW,ISEED,IBOOSS,
     1                  ISUBRO,IBUGA3,IERROR)
C
