C     WRITTEN BY--CODE FOR MANDEL-PAULE, MAXIMUM LIKELIHOOD 
C                 PROVIDED BY MARK VANGEL, BOB BASED ON MACROS
C                 PROVIDED BY STEFAN LEIGH.
C     PRINTING--YES
