C                                       WHERE SOME LABS HAVE 0 STANDARD
C                                       DEVIATION
C     UPDATED  VERSION--OCTOBER   2011. OPTIONAL LABID VARIABLE FOR
C                                       SUMMARY DATA CASE
C     UPDATED         --OCTOBER   2014. FOR SUMMARY DATA, OPTION TO
