      REAL XDLS2
      REAL SEDLK1
      REAL SEDLK2
      REAL SERUK1
      REAL SERUK2
      REAL SEHDK1
      REAL SEHDK2
      REAL XDLK2
      REAL XDLK3
      REAL SEGCI
