C     VERSION NUMBER--2013/8
C     ORIGINAL VERSION--AUGUST    2013.
C
C-----CHARACTER STATEMENTS FOR NON-COMMON VARIABLES-------------------
C
      CHARACTER*4 IBUGA3
      CHARACTER*4 ISUBRO
      CHARACTER*4 IERROR
      CHARACTER*4 ICAPSW
      CHARACTER*4 ICAPTY
      CHARACTER*4 IFORSW
